citation: Proclamation under the Rail Infrastructure Act 2007 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Rail Infrastructure Act 2007

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Rail Infrastructure Act 2007 fix 14 November 2007 as the day on which that Act commences.

5 November 2007

W. J. E. COX

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

J. G. COX

Minister for Infrastructure

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 14 November 2007

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Infrastructure, Energy and Resources.
